narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: TAKE IT TAKE IT TAKE IT!
I would 100% recommend it to any student looking to try a new language. It isn't as difficult as it may seem at first and it will be your favorite class, hands down.

The class is an introduction to Yoruba. You learn pretty much all the same things as you would in any other L1 language class. However the class is so small and you really get to know all of the other students well. Best language choice anyone could make.
